{"tid":1835491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[沒事兒]世衛讚揚中國採措施防武漢肺炎疫情擴散","createTime":"2020-01-23T01:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T06:22:42.000Z","uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6c16e0fdc864a194d7d3fea6ac291eb1d25f9f1d","tid":1835491,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T01:05:27.000Z","msg":"（法新社日內瓦22日電） 世界衛生組織（WHO）今 天表示，中國已採取措施控制新型冠狀病毒引發的武漢 肺炎疫情，這有助將疫情在國際進一步擴散的風險「減 到最小」。 武漢市肺炎疫情防控指揮部已發布通告表示，自今 晨10時起，全市公車、地鐵、輪渡、長途客運暫停運營 ；無特殊原因，市民不要離開武漢，機場、火車站離開 武漢通道暫時關閉。 世衛組織秘書長譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）讚揚這是「非常，非常有力的措施」， 將可「把疫情擴散國際的機會減到最小」。 湖北省的武漢市有1100萬人口，省政府昨晚召開新聞 發布會證實，至22日晚上8時，湖北省累計通報新型冠 狀病毒感染確診病例444例，死亡17例。"},{"pid":"c0ff87317ea7d482867bc983213791f71b3eb140","tid":1835491,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T01:06:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">奶共</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff7d216110a5e87ac9b4cef9dcb975495a0f590","tid":1835491,"uid":104804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c0ff87317ea7d482867bc983213791f71b3eb140","tid":1835491,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T01:06:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">奶共</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T01:07:07.000Z","msg":"世衛只不過係共狗玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd0936124dcfafe94c9ddcfc355169b5d985733","tid":1835491,"uid":180302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T01:07:48.000Z","msg":"一路讚落去 就會死多啲人再支爆"},{"pid":"04631c2f080c9e25b08395bef284eb539fd5d742","tid":1835491,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T01:08:30.000Z","msg":"減到最小(全球都有病例)"},{"pid":"e4974a93124de0dbc1fbd64131955712055928e5","tid":1835491,"uid":392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c0ff87317ea7